name: NOTICE•ME•SENPAI
description: NOTICE•ME•SENPAI is a Rune etched on the Bitcoin blockchain. Inspired by the popular meme deeply rooted in anime, manga and internet culture. Driven by the longing for recognition, this phrase symbolizes the heartfelt and often humorous pursuit of validation. By blending the creativity of anime storytelling with the permanence of Bitcoin Runes, NOTICE ME SENPAI transforms culture into a Bitcoin powered movement.
